    "description": "An M5 train carries a Stable (or LTS) claim only when its per-feature scorecard passes every axis, the proof packet is current within its freshness SLO, any waiver is unexpired, the owner manifest is signed, and its rollback/downgrade automation is defined and verified. A train that loses any of those must drop below the cutline rather than inherit an adjacent qualified train."
  },
